Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.07,0:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,God appears and disappears on command.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I turned on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Some days I fall over, this morning I'm falling over,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have the chair for assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.68,0:02:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We always start the lectures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with a very significant piece of information,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which can save you many lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The primary illusion, the ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.41,0:02:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All the great avatars spoke of a basic ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't really define what the ignorance was,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:03:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to my satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The basic ignorance is, for the intelligent world,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,of which we are a major component,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the basic belief in causality is the stumbling block.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because people get beyond the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Einstein didn't make it, 499, Newton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The great geniuses couldn't get beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the great barrier of the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of a separate, independent person,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,different and separate from God,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on the whole axiom of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All comes into existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of divine ordination.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The unmanifest becoming manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening spontaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,effortlessly and perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as evolution is unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Creation and evolution are one and the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The great infinite energy field,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we all have our existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is happening spontaneously,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.20,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,everything automatically fulfills its karmic potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all happening of its own, with absolute perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It requires no outside agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That we say now is the advancing edge of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We are the product of all of evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,throughout all of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We inherit a potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is called that karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do without karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just be what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You relax into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing to be acquired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only the relinquishment of that which you are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That requires no effort,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but it requires merely a laying back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowing things to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So where do you find the essence of divinity within you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,God is both transcendent,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from a descriptive viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and imminent from an experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,God transcendent is the subject of theology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.03,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God imminent is the subject of the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the scientist is the authority of the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the mystic is the authority of the nonlinear domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,which is completely experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And about which nothing can be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take us all morning to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,how nothing need be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the board?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whiteboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:06:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you cancel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you'll have to have the whiteboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have the whiteboard, Brock?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Brock, we have the whiteboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We can maybe get one from the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't find God without an explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a diagram.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are at the forefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we are at the forefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We are at the forefront of the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as it has evolved through millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the epitome of it in this domain at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have within us a potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.19,0:08:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Education is to inform us about the content
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and has to do with the world of form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.19,0:08:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual reality, which everyone seeks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,when they reach a certain level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,they begin to intuit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they get captivated,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they get captured by the gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They get captured by the gravity of the potential
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of their own future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.53,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People think they're driven by the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not driven by the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're attracted by the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And the future has been set by your own intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The intention to become enlightened, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,is why everybody is here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and why they're all gonna be enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the desire to be enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't be enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the desire to be enlightened, you can't be enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the desire to be enlightened, you can't be enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've heard of it, nothing else will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've heard of it, nothing else will suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said that and that is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said that and that is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody asked already,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between salvation and enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody asked already,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between salvation and enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between salvation and enlightenment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said, much of what we say came about
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As we said, much of what we say came about
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,not only through subjective realization,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but then a verification by advanced techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To an ignorant world, Christ came directly from Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,with no prior human knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in lifetimes to teach salvation that there was an infinite domain of spiritual reality
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and he taught how to avoid what we can only call bad karma to avoid the lower energy fields
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,because there is no death consequently when you leave the body you will really experience that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:10:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,which you are that which you are is in a way self-created through one's own choice and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual intention so he said do not create for yourself once you leave the body regions of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering and misery instead follow these teachings and you will experience the heavenly realms
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.50,0:10:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore the knowingness of that is already within you he said heaven is already within
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.76,0:10:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you and it is only necessary to discover it. So he led the way and showed the way
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,how to discover it. The energy field of that which we call Jesus the Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates at 1,000 which is the highest dimension on our calibrated scale of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. It is very unlikely that the human nervous system can handle an
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,energy field over a thousand and even as it gets near there there's a tendency to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,fall over and get weak and leave the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right so we'll try to what we're actually going to be doing is trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,clarify what Christ said and as you will discover he said avoid anything that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,makes you go weak with kinesiology that's what he said because we discover
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then it calibrates below 200 and makes you go weak with kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is precisely what has been what he defined as sin. So sin is not to be
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,feared not to be dreaded not to be a source of guilt it's to be transcended
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:12:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and avoided because it's a road that leads you to unpleasant places. In this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential infinity which is talking to you today there was the profound
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of the lower depths of hell and I agree with Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They are to be avoided at all costs. Far more dreadful than can be imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because they are outside of time. It's one thing to have a migraine it's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,another have to have a migraine through all eternity. There's no imitrix in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the spontaneous inner awareness that transformed this consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,in total agreement with Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However he's saying in a way that this is a very difficult level. This is a very
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,difficult planet for humans. Life is very difficult and the chance of
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming completely enlightened are slim here because the gravity of our
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,civilization is so powerful. As we finish as we get into the lecture today which
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is actually quite fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it's like you discovered EMC squared and you can't wait to show it to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody. The explanation of all of history you'll understand this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So yes it's gonna be clear as a bell. So what Jesus said is the best thing to do
