Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,100 uneducated tribes is what he was talking to. Couldn't read, spell, had no
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,schooling, illiterate, printing press hadn't been invented yet. You're talking to a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,relatively primitive society and he was also not appreciated for telling the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,truth.
