Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,greed, but then once you've achieved that, you have the courage to start looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So avoid anything that makes you go weak with kinesiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a culture, you know, which is devoted to promoting vulgarity, violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard, I saw a tape by Wayne Dyer the other day, he said that by the time the average
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,child is 12 or 15, something like that, he's already witnessed 58,000 murders, hour after
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he turns off the killing on the television set and gets a video game which teaches him
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,how to kill with greater technical capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The outpouring of the negativity then is immense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So in a society which calibrated at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.03,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, well, I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, to strive for love, and the highest love is unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what he was really saying, the perfect Christian then strives for unconditional love,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and that is the saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To strive for sainthood, and as we'll see when we finally get to some calibrations of
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teachers and all, that Christian sainthood characteristically does occur in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to reach 500 itself is reached by only 4% of the population, and unconditional
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,love is reached by 0.4% of the population.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is practical and feasible in our world, he said, is if you avoid sin, and by meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,worship and forgiveness of others, strive to reach unconditional love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because from unconditional love, from love, from love, one goes to the higher celestial
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,realms, the heavens, when you leave the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can turn that off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha, however, had a different message.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha, although he was speaking in a society where the calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.57,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world was only 90, he came from a pretty sophisticated background.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:19:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment was already ancient in the Vedas, and therefore his audience, which was
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,a more advanced spiritual audience, was capable of reaching for something higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Buddha taught the way to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So as love is 500 to 540, enlightenment, when it occurs, is calibrated at 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha himself went to advanced states of enlightenment, which practically never
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,occurred in history, to 1,000, its ultimate capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of divinity within, as the self, is a realization that occurs about 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is a practical goal, to realize the self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And in recent times, we use Ramana Maharshi and Nisargadatta Maharaj as examples, primarily
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,because they live sufficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently, what they had to say has been taken down verbatim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What Jesus said and what the Buddha said, thousands of years ago, some of it is verifiable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and some of it is not, which we'll get into today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is therefore, you might say, a more ambitious undertaking, and it requires
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.01,0:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,a more intense commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What we teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.62,0:21:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What it's given we have called, devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, to reach enlightenment one has to transcend duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that takes a great devotion, a great devotion to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not devotion to some other being, but devotion to the essence of the truth itself, which
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is already within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.42,0:21:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It means, under appropriate conditions with great intention, one can filamentate it and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,reach a very advanced state of consciousness even within this world therefore both salvation and
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment are possibilities practical possibilities doable except that you don't do it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.23,0:22:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,so how to find the way all right the most direct way is to my studies understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and experiences devotional non-duality why because god cannot be experienced in as a past entity so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,traditional religion will tell you what happened on the other side of the world with some other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.90,0:22:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ethnic group 2 000 years ago under peculiar conditions and how does that help you now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.37,0:22:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're waiting for the bus that's very interesting historically and that has been
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of the way of religion is to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,what should we say not academic but um to put in a rigid form historical events
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened to who where and when backwards in time gets into sort of a deification of geography
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and historic events most of which were more political than spiritual in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,however innate within religion is spiritual truth and some people are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,capable of ignoring the trivialities and focusing on the central truth when people reach a certain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness however they begin seeking the core of spiritual truth for its own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the ultimate reality that is realizable and they begin to seek what is traditionally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.14,0:24:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,called self-realization the awareness that the source of your own existence is within
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore if the discovery is something within there's no point of looking for it in history
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.46,0:24:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or elsewhere there is nothing new to be acquired no new knowledge no new experience it's a matter of
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.76,0:24:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering to what already exists so what needs to be realized that which people are looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.36,0:24:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is already an existent reality and one's devotion to letting go of polygamy and the
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.18,0:24:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritualaniy of the soul of god
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.30,0:24:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,all the obstacles, which is devotional,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.60,0:24:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is letting go all judgmentalism,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.72,0:24:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,all considerations, all dualistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.48,0:24:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,this versus that,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.01,0:25:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowing which already exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.99,0:25:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The most profound awareness as it unfolds
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.77,0:25:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is that divinity is the very source of your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.78,0:25:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So the fast track is to look back of the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.76,0:25:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to try to sense and intuit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.98,0:25:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the source out of which your existence arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.41,0:25:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the source out of which all phenomena arise
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.51,0:25:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is an infinite, is a potentiality becoming manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.92,0:25:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you see, everything is happening spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.96,0:25:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and perfectly of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.50,0:25:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.82,0:25:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The belief in cause will fix you in an idea
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.92,0:25:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that there's a subconsciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.82,0:25:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a separate I, the ego self,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.19,0:25:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that is separate from the infinite I.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.12,0:26:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the whole belief system of causality
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.02,0:26:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is why most people never transcend the 400th.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.01,0:26:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is happening spontaneously
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.68,0:26:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of the fact that it is manifesting
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.25,0:26:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,its potential, its karmic inheritance,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.21,0:26:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,fulfilling its potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.09,0:26:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all a concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.80,0:26:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all occurring in an infinite universe
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.80,0:26:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.98,0:26:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe which we call consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.26,0:26:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,which is beyond form,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.68,0:26:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the non-linear domain beyond form,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.78,0:27:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is the source of infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.45,0:27:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even within the physical domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.44,0:27:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,one cubic centimeter of space
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.76,0:27:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,contains an infinite amount of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.58,0:27:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The potential power in one cubic centimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.60,0:27:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of space, is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.24,0:27:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the field, the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.33,0:27:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is the source of power within the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.88,0:27:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And a field exerts its dominance, its power,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.07,0:27:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,by merely being what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.02,0:27:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to merely be that which it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.23,0:27:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything within it, like little iron filings,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.89,0:27:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically moves in a karmic dance
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.27,0:28:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.82,0:28:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.62,0:28:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other to be dreaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.88,0:28:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite field, then, dominates all within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.04,0:28:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the context, the infinite source of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.04,0:28:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Within, then, the source of joy is not out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.97,0:28:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of joy, then, is the witnessing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.97,0:28:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization, the experience, the knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.97,0:28:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of your existence is the source of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.90,0:28:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is the same source,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.99,0:28:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,as the devotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.99,0:28:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,which drives you through the obstacles of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.30,0:28:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To transcend the ego, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.30,0:29:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,one can save an infinite number of lifetimes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.37,0:29:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,by letting go of the theory of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.39,0:29:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we genuflect before the theory of causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.51,0:29:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see what it calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.37,0:29:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.84,0:29:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality is over 460.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.90,0:29:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,465.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.90,0:29:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,470.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.90,0:29:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The principle of causality is 470.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.67,0:29:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That is wonderful for operating in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.04,0:29:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's science.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.16,0:29:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.55,0:29:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But 470 is a long, long way from enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.55,0:29:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,At 470, you read about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.60,0:29:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As we'll see, the great churches,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.70,0:29:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they started out at 1,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.70,0:29:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and then over time came down into the high 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.76,0:30:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They did so because they were trying to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.76,0:30:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,it, to explain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.14,0:30:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The experience is way beyond 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.14,0:30:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, nothing is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.52,0:30:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As the realization of the source of your experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.00,0:30:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize it's the divinity that is the source
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.00,0:30:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the isness of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.34,0:30:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it just reveals itself in an enormous overwhelm,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.34,0:30:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,which takes you out of the world for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.62,0:30:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how you get back into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.62,0:30:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's say here's a person with a small essence,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a small self,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.07,0:30:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and here we're going to make the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.07,0:30:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of a mini-universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.56,0:30:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which you can't see, which is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.97,0:31:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I get hung up on form?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.53,0:31:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I think somebody washed this with a nice high-gloss polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.53,0:31:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.53,0:31:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there we have the ego, the world of form.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.69,0:31:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we have, with little dots,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.69,0:31:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,an infinite universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.75,0:31:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can save huge amounts of time
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.52,0:31:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,by understanding what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.52,0:31:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world of form,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.25,0:31:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which we witness every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.44,0:31:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,which we identify with as the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.44,0:31:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the self, with a small s.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.44,0:31:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This infinite potentiality is the self with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.05,0:31:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The average person thinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.42,0:31:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I am this, and ignores this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.42,0:31:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The average person thinks my survival is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.87,0:31:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's due to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.87,0:31:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's actually due to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.99,0:31:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your existence is supported by the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.24,0:31:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the best efforts of your ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.24,0:32:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,which it looks for praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.33,0:32:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered the keys to the house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.33,0:32:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What a good boy am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.52,0:32:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I remember the keys to the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.52,0:32:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the spirit, which sustains my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.52,0:32:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then, is a field,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.52,0:32:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,which tends to bring that kind of self-preservation thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.52,0:32:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,up out of the ego, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.32,0:32:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,without
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.32,0:32:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite field,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.89,0:32:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind would have had no reason
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.02,0:32:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to remember the keys to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.02,0:32:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.49,0:32:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,When one lets go thinking that I am this,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.49,0:32:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so you see how causality works.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.49,0:32:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Causality thinks there is a personal I
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.49,0:32:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the cause of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.49,0:32:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Or there's something out there
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.78,0:32:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the cause of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.78,0:32:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.13,0:32:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the average lifetime is spent
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.13,0:32:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,manipulating and struggling
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.13,0:33:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world of duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.41,0:33:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the world of force,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.48,0:33:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,based on the idea of causality.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.70,0:33:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,With the transcendence of identification with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.91,0:33:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,one begins to intuit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.91,0:33:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is a higher field,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.87,0:33:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the letting go of the identification with this itself
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.93,0:33:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to the identification of this itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.93,0:33:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why we tell people,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.85,0:33:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're serious about spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.85,0:33:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,make sure you have friends that know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.85,0:33:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.85,0:33:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that in some lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.29,0:33:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got a worried letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.29,0:33:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we do that, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.29,0:33:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because intense meditation,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.52,0:33:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,plus really merely hearing of higher truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.52,0:33:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,can transport you rather rapidly past
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.52,0:33:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.68,0:33:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you find yourself in a state
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.68,0:34:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that can only be described as what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.54,0:34:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Classically, it's called bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.46,0:34:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In that state, one really,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.48,0:34:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,from a physical viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.92,0:34:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is relatively immobilized.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.98,0:34:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.87,0:34:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the volition has gone out of,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.87,0:34:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,out of running it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.04,0:34:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not me,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.04,0:34:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes like a piece of furniture
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.04,0:34:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of no particular interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.07,0:34:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people may entreat you
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.07,0:34:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to come back in the body and reactivate it,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.07,0:34:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's best to ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.80,0:34:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They think you've died, let them grieve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.89,0:34:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there is no death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.91,0:34:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not possible for life
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.96,0:34:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.96,0:34:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The law of the conservation of energy of matter
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.96,0:35:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and energy applies to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.15,0:35:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is the source,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.40,0:35:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the very source and essence of existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.40,0:35:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,can hardly have a beginning or an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.40,0:35:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is all-encompassing
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.36,0:35:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,can only transform from this into that,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.36,0:35:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but it cannot cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.36,0:35:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not have the power within itself
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.80,0:35:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to create its own existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.80,0:35:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,nor does it have within itself
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.80,0:35:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the option to cease its own existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.80,0:35:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,because the source and the control of existence
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.54,0:35:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,does not belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.54,0:35:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.65,0:35:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to have any say about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.65,0:35:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The upside of that is
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.24,0:35:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't get to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.58,0:35:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,even your own physical death.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.58,0:36:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said, the karmic destination
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.09,0:36:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is already set at the time of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.09,0:36:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of death is already set.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.02,0:36:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As people are born,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.32,0:36:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they already have a calibrated level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.89,0:36:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So if people don't believe in karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.89,0:36:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,they will have to explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.11,0:36:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,However, then we know that the spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.20,0:36:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,enters the embryo in the third month.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.91,0:36:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First, you're born with a calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.91,0:36:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,right from birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.52,0:36:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirit, the entity from our own consciousness research,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.52,0:36:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,enters the embryo at age three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.52,0:36:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,After that time, it waits to see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.52,0:36:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's going to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.52,0:36:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This bus is going to get there
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.52,0:36:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,before it gets on the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.60,0:36:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the time of expiration of this physicality
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.60,0:36:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is already set at the time of birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.60,0:36:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The time of birth is already set.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.80,0:36:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At that particular event,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.80,0:37:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not possible to experience one's physical death
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.80,0:37:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're instantly out of the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.12,0:37:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You witnessed the physicality down there
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.12,0:37:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and you didn't die at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.53,0:37:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disappointing for a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.52,0:37:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything we said.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.97,0:37:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We verify anything that may be
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.97,0:37:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhat in conflict with popular belief systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.97,0:37:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, if what I'm saying isn't in conflict
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.60,0:37:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with many belief systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.60,0:37:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you know I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.17,0:37:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if the truth were prevalent,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.17,0:37:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody would be enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.23,0:37:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extremely rare, consequently.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.29,0:37:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What the world believes primarily
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.29,0:37:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is primarily fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.38,0:37:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness level of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.38,0:37:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,was 190 until the late 1980s
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.38,0:37:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when it suddenly jumped to 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.20,0:37:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, it's a new level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.32,0:38:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.89,0:38:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With profound implications for life,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.89,0:38:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, here on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.28,0:38:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, nothing that happens
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.28,0:38:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,has a cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is coming about
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.85,0:38:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as the advancing edge
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.32,0:38:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of creation, evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.32,0:38:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,as the spontaneous interaction
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.32,0:38:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.44,0:38:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,both linear and non-linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.36,0:38:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,back through infinite time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.36,0:38:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is infinite
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.64,0:38:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,has no beginning nor end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.64,0:38:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One time a student in the back of the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.98,0:39:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,said,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.48,0:39:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher, teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.48,0:39:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when did you say the world was ending?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.68,0:39:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And the teacher said,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.68,0:39:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a hundred trillions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.84,0:39:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, oh my god,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.84,0:39:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said a hundred billion.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.87,0:39:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what most people worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.87,0:39:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The trivial idiocies and irrelevancies of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.87,0:39:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And many religions fall into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.87,0:39:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They're more worried about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.87,0:39:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of shoelaces to wear,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.87,0:39:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and whether they wear a hat
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.87,0:39:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,or don't wear a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.87,0:39:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And completely ignore
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.87,0:39:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the crucial spiritual truth, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.87,0:39:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.38,0:39:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll look at the sad story
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.38,0:39:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world's religions in a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.44,0:39:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's just have
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.22,0:39:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the Calvary level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.22,0:39:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And we want to just reaffirm,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.95,0:39:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.72,0:39:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,anything from here down
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.72,0:39:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,makes you go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.72,0:39:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything from here up
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.93,0:39:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,makes you go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.93,0:40:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The response
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.57,0:40:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is an impersonal response
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.57,0:40:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.57,0:40:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness itself
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.02,0:40:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is an expression of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.02,0:40:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and life recognizes truth
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.02,0:40:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.02,0:40:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And it fails to recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.14,0:40:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is adverse to life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.14,0:40:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and which has no intrinsic reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.14,0:40:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore the arm goes weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.14,0:40:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The theory of evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.09,0:40:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,also calibrates around 460.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.09,0:40:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's an explanation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.41,0:40:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,which satisfies the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.41,0:40:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But a group like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.02,0:40:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,your problem is not your intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.02,0:40:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is to transcend the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.47,0:40:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.79,0:40:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,at a very advanced level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.79,0:40:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which is the high,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.79,0:40:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,most people are in the,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.79,0:40:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,considerably into the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.79,0:40:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.62,0:40:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll just continue that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.62,0:40:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll go on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.62,0:40:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to some more interesting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.23,0:40:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do that next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.52,0:40:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just recapitulating
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.52,0:41:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,previous lectures here
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.52,0:41:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for people who haven't been here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.55,0:41:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And because we all want to start out
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.55,0:41:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.55,0:41:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We said that the basic principle
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.80,0:41:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the divisive factor
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.80,0:41:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that keeps the ego going
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.80,0:41:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is its capacity to think
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.80,0:41:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,in terms of duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.70,0:41:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The pathway of devotional non-duality
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.70,0:41:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,then is,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.70,0:41:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,means how to transcend
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.70,0:41:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,dualistic thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.99,0:41:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Either or,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.99,0:41:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,good and bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.99,0:41:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,war and peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.02,0:41:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,As we demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.02,0:41:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in previous lectures,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.02,0:41:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,war is not the opposite of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.02,0:41:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.02,0:41:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,peace is the opposite of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.66,0:41:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea of creating
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.66,0:41:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,artificial dualities,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.66,0:41:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,which exist only as mentations
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.66,0:41:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,within the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.92,0:41:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,These dualities are only a mentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.89,0:41:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And to demonstrate this,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.89,0:41:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we point that opposite,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.08,0:41:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that hot is not the opposite of cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.08,0:41:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are varying degrees
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.08,0:42:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,of the presence of heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.15,0:42:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's arbitrary to say
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.15,0:42:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,this is hot and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.15,0:42:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's quite obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.15,0:42:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.15,0:42:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one variable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.40,0:42:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a fact
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.40,0:42:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in all dualistic thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.40,0:42:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's actually only one variable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.81,0:42:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In linguistic convenience,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.94,0:42:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we have divided it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.96,0:42:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.96,0:42:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no such reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.70,0:42:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has absolute reality
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.70,0:42:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,can only be proven subjectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.99,0:42:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.99,0:42:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the newest book is called
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.99,0:42:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.52,0:42:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality and Subjectivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.52,0:42:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because reality can only be known
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.52,0:42:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,as subjectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.58,0:42:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So dualistic is a way of talking about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.58,0:42:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not a way of being it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.19,0:42:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's use value.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.19,0:42:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see again,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.19,0:42:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,this has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.22,0:42:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,how it looks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.22,0:42:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the opposite of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.22,0:42:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And what somebody thinks
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.44,0:42:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is an ugly-looking alley
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.44,0:43:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,can look to somebody else
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.44,0:43:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,like an artistic presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.44,0:43:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so we're done with all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.73,0:43:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.73,0:43:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I wanted to show
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.89,0:43:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the last one in this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.89,0:43:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.89,0:43:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we've done now
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.47,0:43:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is recapitulate how we got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.04,0:43:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a girl
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.04,0:43:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at the girl's rehab place that I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.30,0:43:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And all she says is,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.30,0:43:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.30,0:43:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.30,0:43:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.30,0:43:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.30,0:43:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All our girls say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.30,0:43:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.30,0:43:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.46,0:43:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.46,0:43:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I made her draw this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.46,0:43:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And she actually did this freehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.46,0:43:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.46,0:43:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.46,0:43:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.46,0:43:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I want out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.46,0:43:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me them bananas.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.46,0:43:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.46,0:43:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.46,0:43:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The harder you reach for the bananas,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.46,0:43:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the tighter you are against the bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.46,0:43:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you shout,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.46,0:43:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,yell,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.46,0:43:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hit people,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.46,0:43:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,cut yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.46,0:43:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,threaten people,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.84,0:43:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see you're tightening your imprisonment.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.84,0:43:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually you're going to flatten yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.04,0:43:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,up against the bars.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.04,0:44:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.80,0:44:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely paralyzed by their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.54,0:44:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So here is the unsophisticated basis of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.76,0:44:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.76,0:44:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the grabbing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.01,0:44:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,which comes out of the animal evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.24,0:44:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.49,0:44:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So I said to the girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.49,0:44:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.49,0:44:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that the door to the cage is over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.49,0:44:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.81,0:44:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to turn your back
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.81,0:44:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,on the solar plexus demanding this,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.81,0:44:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,of I wanting this,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.32,0:44:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and become what this place is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.93,0:44:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,To learn how to behave,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.93,0:44:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,learn how to control yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.93,0:44:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,learn how to be responsible,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.93,0:44:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,learn something of the milk of human kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.44,0:44:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the door is open to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.73,0:44:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.73,0:44:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The door is open all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.73,0:44:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The door has never been closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.99,0:44:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.99,0:45:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,when they reach a certain level of improvement,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.99,0:45:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,they're automatically discharged.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.99,0:45:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.99,0:45:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't even stay there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.99,0:45:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Their agency pulls them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the way it is with enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.33,0:45:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not something you can reach for
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.33,0:45:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and strive to get,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.59,0:45:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is already a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.59,0:45:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and the door is already open.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.72,0:45:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.55,0:45:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was her contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.55,0:45:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She did it freehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.96,0:45:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thank her for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.96,0:45:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I made many copies for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.96,0:45:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd use it someday for something,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.96,0:45:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and this morning it came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.02,0:45:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.02,0:45:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So everybody knows the way to enlightenment now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.02,0:45:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's merely a surrendering
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.18,0:45:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of all opinionation, positionalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.18,0:45:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And remember this, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.72,0:45:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Judgmentalism is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.79,0:45:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.79,0:46:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the circuitous way the ego can grab you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.79,0:46:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a letter from a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.92,0:46:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She said,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.92,0:46:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you use bad language?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.92,0:46:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.92,0:46:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she say bad language?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.92,0:46:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, bad language.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.10,0:46:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I never heard myself use bad language.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.10,0:46:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.10,0:46:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going to be said
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.10,0:46:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,until I hear it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.88,0:46:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So she goes to a lecture on non-duality,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.88,0:46:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,letting go of judgmentalism,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.88,0:46:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and tells me my speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.98,0:46:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I use bad language.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.98,0:46:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get a kick out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.28,0:46:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the bad language about?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.28,0:46:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.28,0:46:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,we've got our perceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.76,0:46:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.76,0:46:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain I thought it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.28,0:46:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.28,0:46:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's men and women,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.28,0:46:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.28,0:46:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And what sounds meaningful
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.38,0:46:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and sinks home with a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.38,0:46:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to a guy who's going to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.38,0:46:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that was really airy-fairy, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.38,0:46:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.96,0:47:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all peaches and cream and flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.96,0:47:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it sounds sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.96,0:47:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the real world?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.34,0:47:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So occasionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.34,0:47:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I use language that's masculine
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.34,0:47:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because it pulls out of your gut
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.34,0:47:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.34,0:47:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.34,0:47:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That word gets,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.34,0:47:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get what you mean, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.34,0:47:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I could say it's inadvisable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.96,0:47:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not totally acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.96,0:47:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.31,0:47:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they had the History Channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.31,0:47:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the story of Ivan the Terrible,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.31,0:47:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the worst stories in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.72,0:47:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at Susie and I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.76,0:47:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His behavior was not really too desirable, Susie.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.43,0:47:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, occasionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.81,0:47:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you've got to speak to the masculine
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.81,0:47:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because there's a gut way of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.29,0:47:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.29,0:47:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,that the woman doesn't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.29,0:47:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a glance between two guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.52,0:47:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and in that,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.52,0:47:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a complete understanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.52,0:48:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.52,0:48:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You get what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.52,0:48:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your moment to climb the mast, Shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.86,0:48:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're terrified is your crap, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.06,0:48:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Shorty didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.18,0:48:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He got to the top and had to be rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.18,0:48:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But the guy knows what that means, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.47,0:48:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it isn't a woman's language.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.72,0:48:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the guy goes like that with his foot,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.72,0:48:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,it already has a meaning in his culture
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.72,0:48:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and his background.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.72,0:48:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the woman goes like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.98,0:48:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that has a meaning in her culture and background.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.98,0:48:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I spent a lot of time learning about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.56,0:48:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.56,0:48:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that's insignificant tripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.56,0:48:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.56,0:49:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's where they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.26,0:49:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.53,0:49:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.53,0:49:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but that kind of a remark is,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.14,0:49:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.14,0:49:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.14,0:49:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.14,0:49:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.14,0:49:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's where men live.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.14,0:49:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.14,0:49:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you will have to forgive me for using
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.49,0:49:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the best bad language I can think of at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.07,0:49:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My function is to communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.07,0:49:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.07,0:49:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.42,0:49:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it isn't a,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.42,0:49:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a doingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.52,0:49:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.52,0:49:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.92,0:49:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it happens of its own anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.92,0:49:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.92,0:49:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be responsible for what's said anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.92,0:49:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's said until it's said.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.20,0:49:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to watch the time
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.20,0:49:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,because we've got a lot of tremendous stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.20,0:49:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to cover this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.20,0:49:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather earth-shaking and,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.43,0:49:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.43,0:49:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,we better get to the earth-shaking world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.43,0:49:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start with the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.43,0:50:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.43,0:50:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been working for,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.43,0:50:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,some months,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.43,0:50:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as soon as I've been working.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.43,0:50:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.43,0:50:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of every country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.43,0:50:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We then proceeded to do every continent.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.88,0:50:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We then proceeded to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.97,0:50:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,now,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.45,0:50:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so for simple explanation,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.45,0:50:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,almost all of history and current events
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.51,0:50:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly becomes obvious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.54,0:50:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize that man has been trying to navigate
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.54,0:50:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,without a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.40,0:50:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How diplomatic course,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.40,0:50:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.40,0:50:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,how statesmen can deal with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.40,0:50:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when they don't even know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.40,0:50:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what they're dealing with is beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.40,0:50:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It would lead to endless catastrophe,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.40,0:50:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,war, revolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.40,0:50:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.76,0:50:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.92,0:50:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,just like the invention of the telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.39,0:50:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,allowed amazing discoveries,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.39,0:50:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or E equals MC squared,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.39,0:50:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,allows amazing discoveries,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.39,0:50:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,some discoveries are seminal
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.39,0:50:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and open up whole dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.39,0:51:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the Western Hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.93,0:51:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated the level of the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.93,0:51:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,of these particular areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.93,0:51:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's big enough that you can all see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.44,0:51:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we look up at Greenland and 345.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.44,0:51:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Iceland, I think, is somewhat less than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.44,0:51:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a lot of alcoholism there.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.44,0:51:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I think half the population is alcoholic in Iceland.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.44,0:51:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So that would be why it's somewhat lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.44,0:51:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at North America,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.44,0:51:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you see Canada's about five points,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.44,0:51:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,10 points less than the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.44,0:51:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the general area you see is 410 to 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.44,0:51:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's education,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.44,0:51:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that's science,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.51,0:51:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that's reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.51,0:51:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,rationality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.51,0:51:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the laws we live by
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.60,0:51:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and we presume everybody else lives by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.92,0:51:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we get to the Central America,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.92,0:51:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the 300s.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.92,0:51:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enthusiasm,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.92,0:51:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,building big cement plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.14,0:51:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impressive what they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.14,0:52:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's industry and forthrightness.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.33,0:52:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you've got South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.75,0:52:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It runs generally 285 to 310.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.75,0:52:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important of all this is it's all over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.75,0:52:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.75,0:52:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're relatively safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.75,0:52:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,People may screw up down here with the Falkland Islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.75,0:52:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to put them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.75,0:52:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to some mad person,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.94,0:52:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's just bad judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.20,0:52:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a violently explosive hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.20,0:52:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only got one place here you've got to worry about
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.23,0:52:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're too weak and at the bottom of the barrel
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.23,0:52:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to worry about them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.23,0:52:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're at 55 and that's Haiti.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.23,0:52:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Haiti can't do much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.92,0:52:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you pour more money into Haiti,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.92,0:52:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the only thing that happens is the birth rate goes up
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.92,0:52:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and poverty and starvation goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.92,0:52:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So something other than cash,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.34,0:52:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been tried and everybody decided
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.34,0:52:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't help any.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.50,0:52:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kind of people are also quite subject to
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.50,0:52:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,sadistic rule by a dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.66,0:53:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A sadistic dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.66,0:53:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I don't know anything about the history of Haiti,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.69,0:53:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you this place is probably
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.69,0:53:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,currently or recently run
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.69,0:53:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,by a sadistic dictator
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.69,0:53:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,who exploits the people,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.69,0:53:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,allows them to starve
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.69,0:53:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and probably just kills them for amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.69,0:53:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is probably pretty accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.69,0:53:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, where's the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.84,0:53:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we'll get to more serious considerations.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.94,0:53:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We look at the other hemisphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.94,0:53:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw Australia 410, intelligent, rational, educated.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.25,0:53:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we start getting up higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.44,0:53:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You see Korea in the 400s,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.86,0:53:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan, they're all pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.86,0:53:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,India, 355.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.89,0:53:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see Madagascar, 125.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.89,0:53:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,South Africa, 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.89,0:53:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you see the real trouble coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.89,0:53:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is all of Africa, about 40 to 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.56,0:54:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And North Africa, 70 to 185.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.72,0:54:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we will see the difficulty arises
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.30,0:54:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,between latitude 10 to 40 north
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.30,0:54:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,in North Africa
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.30,0:54:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is where you're going to see all the problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.30,0:54:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You see Russia,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.52,0:54:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then you see Mongolia,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.52,0:54:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you see China at 305,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.52,0:54:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan at 355.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.52,0:54:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.35,0:54:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.35,0:54:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.80,0:54:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we've got maps with greater detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.80,0:54:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to simplify it so you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.80,0:54:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you're looking at North Africa about 175
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.80,0:54:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're looking at the Near East.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.80,0:54:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.80,0:54:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How much will democracy appeal
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.87,0:54:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to people who calibrated 55?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.87,0:54:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't even got water.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.54,0:54:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have bathrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.83,0:54:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have food.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.83,0:54:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your children are dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.08,0:54:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,falling over with AIDS and starvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.08,0:55:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is interested in political systems?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.81,0:55:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They will naturally follow anybody
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.23,0:55:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who gives them food and water.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.23,0:55:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy to become a dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.85,0:55:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You just steal from the weak
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.65,0:55:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and use that to control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.65,0:55:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And you give it back to them for a trickle
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.65,0:55:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and in turn for their worship and servitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.65,0:55:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so here we have this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.09,0:55:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.12,0:55:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.12,0:55:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.44,0:55:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is too complicated, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.44,0:55:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The original of this took me a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.44,0:55:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It took us a week, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.44,0:55:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A whole weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.50,0:55:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we calibrated every country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.50,0:55:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I took the names of the countries out
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.50,0:55:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,because you wouldn't be able to read anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.92,0:55:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you can see what you're dealing with.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.92,0:55:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're in the State Department
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.92,0:55:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say we're going to deal with
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.92,0:55:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,such and such country in such and such region,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.92,0:56:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you better know what the hell you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.19,0:56:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated level of consciousness 70
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.19,0:56:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,has nothing to do with 421.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.19,0:56:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.05,0:56:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They slaughter each other here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.05,0:56:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They just slaughter each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.17,0:56:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not even up to slavery yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.23,0:56:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Slavery, 70 you get,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.23,0:56:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the people just vanquished are worth money on the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.23,0:56:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,These people aren't even there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.23,0:56:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They just slaughter them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.23,0:56:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They take over a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.23,0:56:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They kill everybody in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.32,0:56:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's North Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.38,0:56:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.38,0:56:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Europe is in the 300s,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.38,0:56:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,340s, 400.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.38,0:56:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the big problem areas of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.48,0:56:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't know anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.89,0:56:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,don't read the newspaper at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.89,0:56:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and you look at this, you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.89,0:56:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,uh-oh, I can see where the problems
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.02,0:56:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are likely to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.02,0:56:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was embarrassed by
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.95,0:56:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the way an American interviewer
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.95,0:56:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,interviewed the President of China.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.95,0:57:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,President of China, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.65,0:57:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,is much higher than 305,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.65,0:57:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,way up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.88,0:57:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Insulting, saying to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.88,0:57:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,look what's wrong with your culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.16,0:57:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,civil rights and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.58,0:57:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.54,0:57:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Antagonizing the people
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.54,0:57:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,acting like we're better than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.54,0:57:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.83,0:57:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't the way to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.83,0:57:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have the next
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.96,0:57:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,sad story here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.84,0:57:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.84,0:57:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that you got the overall picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.84,0:57:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,because people ask me,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.91,0:57:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what the names of the various countries are,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.91,0:57:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, so I put this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.00,0:57:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the names of the countries, ask me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.00,0:57:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sudan, 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.12,0:57:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rwanda, 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.12,0:57:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenya, 70.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.21,0:57:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanzania, 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.21,0:57:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Zambia, 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.21,0:57:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Angola, 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.37,0:57:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Namibia, 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.82,0:58:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Zimbabwe, 80.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.82,0:58:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Botswana, 65.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.27,0:58:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nigeria, 75.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.27,0:58:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Chad, 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.27,0:58:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the size of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.27,0:58:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ethiopia,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.33,0:58:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,one something or other.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.19,0:58:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Somalia, 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.19,0:58:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.21,0:58:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's North Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.50,0:58:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's look up to an even sadder story.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.50,0:58:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Middle East.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.79,0:58:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.79,0:58:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,these people are not a danger to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.79,0:58:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,At 50, you can't get your act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.79,0:58:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have hardly clothes to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.79,0:58:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not much of a danger to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.25,0:58:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But now,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.25,0:58:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,when you start rising up a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.25,0:58:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting a little bit of power,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.25,0:58:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you give people with a caveman mentality
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.25,0:58:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a gun, now you've got problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.25,0:58:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you giving a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.76,0:58:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,People with a mentality up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.15,0:58:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,180, 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.15,0:58:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'll find,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.15,0:59:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, look over on the right, I got it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.15,0:59:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the current calibration?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.24,0:59:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We change these calibrations
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.24,0:59:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.63,0:59:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As of maybe a week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.63,0:59:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,this is where it all was a week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.63,0:59:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Israel, 185.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.63,0:59:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Palestine, 165.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.63,0:59:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Saudi Arabia, 175.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.63,0:59:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Iraq, 160.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.72,0:59:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,United Arab Emirates, 180.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.72,0:59:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Jordan, 185.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.72,0:59:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Iran, 190.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.72,0:59:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Iraq, 125.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.13,0:59:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Syria, 120.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.13,0:59:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only hope in the region, Turkey, 245.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.95,0:59:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.04,0:59:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what good a peace parade will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.52,0:59:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.99,0:59:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one was this week's Time Magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.99,0:59:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,While I was doing all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.05,0:59:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we just reached its completion
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.05,1:00:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,this week.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.66,1:00:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I opened Time Magazine,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.66,1:00:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they must have had spies.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.70,1:00:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From 10 to 40 degrees
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.92,1:00:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,north latitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.72,1:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,10 to 40 degrees north latitude.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.75,1:00:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is what I said already, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.75,1:00:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the question is,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.45,1:00:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,should the missionaries go in and,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.45,1:00:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, that was the topic.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.45,1:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are exactly the same countries,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.45,1:00:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,exactly the same war area.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.45,1:00:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.57,1:00:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,mind with potential
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.14,1:00:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,problems. The question was,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.62,1:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,should the Christian missionaries go in there
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.62,1:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and convert these people?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.29,1:00:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Which I thought was hysterically funny.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.29,1:00:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they'll get executed
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.55,1:00:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,for doing so, but aside from that,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.55,1:00:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it brings up
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.55,1:00:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the corollary.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.58,1:00:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't the Islamic people be over in America
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.58,1:00:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to convert us to Islam?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.58,1:01:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.49,1:01:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when we talk about spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.26,1:01:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,community, we want to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.58,1:01:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the world, the condition of the world?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.58,1:01:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in it, but not of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.56,1:01:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.38,1:01:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,directly? Well, if you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.38,1:01:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,deal with,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.57,1:01:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,if you deal with this invisible
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.57,1:01:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,diagram here,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.92,1:01:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if you come at it directly,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.92,1:01:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see the difficulty you're going to have.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.92,1:01:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To use force, then,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.21,1:01:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to have a limited response.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.21,1:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to transform
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.91,1:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the people and turn them into
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.91,1:01:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,saintly peaceniks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.91,1:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They make their living by war.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.80,1:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They get their status from war.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.80,1:01:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They get their sense of
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.84,1:01:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,masculinity, sufficiency.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.84,1:02:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And even now, their spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.99,1:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,belief system is just tied up
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.99,1:02:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with violence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.04,1:02:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it does not seem to me
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.04,1:02:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that addressing it directly is going to have
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.04,1:02:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,very salutary
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.04,1:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,results.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.04,1:02:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't approach
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.72,1:02:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,a thing with force in the level
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.72,1:02:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,of form, then how
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.78,1:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,can you transform
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.81,1:02:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it? Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.55,1:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,by addressing the level
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.55,1:02:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of power, not the level of force.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.55,1:02:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go in there and try to force
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.55,1:02:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you to change your belief systems,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.55,1:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and force you to adopt mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.55,1:02:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and if I don't,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.71,1:02:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you don't,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.71,1:02:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll execute you,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.77,1:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that's going to have a very limited benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.24,1:02:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so if I want to influence
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.24,1:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,something that is not touchable,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.24,1:02:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really touch that
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.24,1:02:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,system, can you? You can't really touch it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.24,1:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,without it blowing back at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.92,1:03:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Force creates counter-force.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.92,1:03:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not going to
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.55,1:03:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,save the world. What can
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.96,1:03:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,we do then, as a spiritual community,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.96,1:03:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if we are all one as humans,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.96,1:03:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is by letting go
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.38,1:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,our own egoistic positionalities,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.38,1:03:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,we reinforce
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.41,1:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.80,1:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, by quantum mechanics,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.80,1:03:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have that formula with us today.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.00,1:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't behave, I'll get it out and show it to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.00,1:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quantum mechanics, we showed
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.00,1:03:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that the collapse of the wave function,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.00,1:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,by the collapse of the wave function,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.58,1:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,by spiritual intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.28,1:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,via the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.28,1:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and Neumann manifestation of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.28,1:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as a collapse of the wave function,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.35,1:03:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we change the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.35,1:03:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We change the field.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.67,1:03:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's say
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.92,1:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,human-ness is highly
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.92,1:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,visible as structure,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.92,1:03:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this thing-ness here,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.40,1:04:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,which is behaving very well today.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.49,1:04:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There is this thing-ness here,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.41,1:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and then around it we could say
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.41,1:04:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,there's mentalization as we advance.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.41,1:04:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The animal doesn't do much in the way of
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.41,1:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,mentalization, but as he gets
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.08,1:04:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,more advanced, he gets more mentalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.08,1:04:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he gets intuitive knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.08,1:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And some animals
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.15,1:04:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,get to be pretty advanced.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.15,1:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Some animals
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.66,1:04:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,get more advanced than humans.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.66,1:04:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not intellectually,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.72,1:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.04,1:04:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said in the book, you're safer with Coco,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.04,1:04:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the gorilla,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.20,1:04:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,than you are with any of these people from the Near East.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.20,1:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Coco will not turn on you,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.86,1:04:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,will not deceive you, will not lie to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.86,1:04:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,will not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.89,1:04:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When you turn your back, you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.37,1:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're capable of being honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.68,1:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's that famous African
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.68,1:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,gray parrot
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.26,1:04:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,at the University in
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.74,1:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Arizona, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.74,1:05:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Also very honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.00,1:05:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't get it to lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.06,1:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue ball, red sponge,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.06,1:05:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,soap.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.06,1:05:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Incapable of deception.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.06,1:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.05,1:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get mentation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.05,1:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We get up to the 400s, we get mentation.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.05,1:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can say there's an energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.05,1:05:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,not physical.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.05,1:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It registers in the physical and activates the brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.05,1:05:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain is a response
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.30,1:05:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,system to energy fields, and
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.30,1:05:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.28,1:05:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,receiver of
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.28,1:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,thought forms.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.28,1:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The thought forms are extremely high frequency,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.28,1:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,not reduplicable
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.57,1:05:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,within the physical realm,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.57,1:05:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but sufficiently powerful
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.05,1:05:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,to activate neuronal
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.05,1:05:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,imprinting and
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.24,1:05:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,memorization, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.24,1:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.65,1:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,intelligence then and mentation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.65,1:06:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,creates like another field around this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.65,1:06:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And then comes spiritual awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.65,1:06:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And the first one
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.94,1:06:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,identifies here, then here, then
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.94,1:06:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,here, then identifies with this here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.94,1:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When you stop identifying
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.80,1:06:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,with this and identify with
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.80,1:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the field, you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.80,1:06:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the source of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.80,1:06:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because at 600, one goes
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.80,1:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,into a state of profound bliss.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.80,1:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.86,1:06:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no words.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.99,1:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.05,1:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only the allness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.93,1:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of an infinite, exquisite
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.59,1:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,presence as
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.59,1:06:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the very essence of love itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.59,1:06:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.12,1:06:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the end of the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.04,1:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The best thing to do at that point,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.04,1:06:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing as you've lost interest in breathing,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.04,1:06:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is to forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.84,1:07:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The bliss state at 600.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.93,1:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we say to people
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.93,1:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that are serious about spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.09,1:07:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,let people that are somewhat spiritually
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.09,1:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,sophisticated be aware, and
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.09,1:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,if you go into such a state,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.18,1:07:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,they should just smile at you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.18,1:07:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and pray with you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.18,1:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and be happy for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.10,1:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, they may call the police,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.10,1:07:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,they may call the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.10,1:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,they may call for a psychiatrist,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.26,1:07:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who won't know what the heck it's all about.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.26,1:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As it approaches,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.60,1:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it becomes like euphoria.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.60,1:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a gladness, a happiness, a joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.60,1:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And this can reach
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.92,1:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,states of high ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.92,1:07:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So one can also go into states
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.92,1:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of high ecstasy,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.98,1:07:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,which can be confused with
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.98,1:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,mania, religious mania.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.98,1:07:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So I think in the last book,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.17,1:07:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave two columns,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.17,1:07:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,how to differentiate a true spiritual state
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.17,1:07:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,from various psychiatric conditions.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.17,1:07:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was a consultant
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.17,1:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to many dioceses,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.65,1:08:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Catholic and Episcopal
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.65,1:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and Zen monastery and all,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.65,1:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,they would sometimes send a monk to me
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.65,1:08:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and they didn't know, is this guy enlightened
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.03,1:08:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or is he catatonic?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.03,1:08:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be hard to tell that for an unsophisticated layman,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.03,1:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.35,1:08:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And having gone into such states,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.02,1:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,also I could see where the police
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.02,1:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,would come and get you
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.02,1:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you just sit on this rock
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.02,1:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no reason to move
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.66,1:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the state is complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.69,1:08:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of the completeness of the state.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.69,1:08:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no desire or thought
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.69,1:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to do or be anything else
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.69,1:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,than what is.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.69,1:08:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is total and complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.36,1:08:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,As a day or two went by,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.36,1:08:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the passers-by might notify the police
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.36,1:08:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you might get dragged off for observation.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.55,1:08:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's best to have somebody aware
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.55,1:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that, hey, he meditates a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.55,1:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.55,1:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he meditates a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.40,1:09:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he wishes to leave the body,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.82,1:09:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we will allow him to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.82,1:09:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's against Medicare rules, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.01,1:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I really quit going to the
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.88,1:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,nursing homes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.88,1:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.20,1:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All these people who want to leave the body so badly.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.20,1:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.45,1:09:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's tubes into everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.45,1:09:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's on wheels.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.22,1:09:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.22,1:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lost interest and all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.22,1:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's please let me die is what it wants.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.22,1:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So they go, the little old lady
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.22,1:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,you can hear in any nursing home.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.22,1:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.65,1:09:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it you want to help us with,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.04,1:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.04,1:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.04,1:09:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against the law
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.71,1:09:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow them to expire.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.03,1:09:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Against their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.03,1:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You would think they would have the right of decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.03,1:10:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's against their wishes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.34,1:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They have to be hydrated.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.34,1:10:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tubes stuck in everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.24,1:10:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't swallow it, they'll put a tube down your...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.93,1:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because Medicare
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.03,1:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,believes that when you die, you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.03,1:10:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore they get excited about all that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.92,1:10:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So you go from identifying
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.92,1:10:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,with this to identifying with mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.92,1:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,all this mental energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.04,1:10:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you begin to intuit
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.04,1:10:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel the energy,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.04,1:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,feel the spirit around you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.56,1:10:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go of the identification with this
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.56,1:10:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and it can happen in a sudden second.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.56,1:10:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,In a sudden second.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.56,1:10:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One tenth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.56,1:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, how long does it take to get enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.56,1:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One tenth of a second, frankly.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.62,1:10:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The next instant,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.97,1:10:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,everything has become technicolor,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.97,1:10:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,3D and incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.29,1:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, one stays in this state.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.29,1:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,50% never come back
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.38,1:11:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.38,1:11:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,50% never survive physically.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.38,1:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,50% will not
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.64,1:11:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,breathe again
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.01,1:11:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize that it's idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.01,1:11:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Or at that point, there is no choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.01,1:11:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So when it happens, it isn't like
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.01,1:11:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.06,1:11:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If enough energy gets put in from here,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.06,1:11:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you maybe get pulled back into identifying
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.06,1:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with this thinkingness here
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.06,1:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and fall for choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.28,1:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's best to avoid relatives.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.64,1:11:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One then spaces out and becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.64,1:11:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not this, I am this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:38.64,1:11:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization of the self
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.04,1:11:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the infinite reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.04,1:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the very source of all of existence
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.04,1:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which all of mankind arises.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.11,1:11:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity is the core and the essence
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.11,1:11:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.00,1:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much takes you out of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.00,1:12:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,for some years.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.00,1:12:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's best to have a fallback plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.36,1:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Traditionally,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.85,1:12:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,people as they get into
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.85,1:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,really serious advanced spiritual work
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.85,1:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,have gathered together in ashrams,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.85,1:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual communities.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.77,1:12:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Our spiritual community is the people
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.77,1:12:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,who show up here and we know each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.77,1:12:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all know that we're involved in this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.12,1:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So the good doctor there passes over
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.12,1:12:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,into the state of bliss.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.48,1:12:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife calls me and I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.48,1:12:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah, he's fine, me and Bea,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.48,1:12:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go over and enjoy with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.05,1:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We know each other to some degree.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.05,1:12:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't have to congregate
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.05,1:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,geographically in a secluded area
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.05,1:12:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which has been a traditional way of doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.05,1:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty then,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.66,1:12:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it's actually not a difficulty,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.66,1:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,it has to do with the karmic
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.66,1:12:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.14,1:12:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, contract.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.14,1:12:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an option or a contract?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.26,1:13:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.68,1:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.15,1:13:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there was the option.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.82,1:13:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There was not the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.82,1:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was an option.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.98,1:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There was
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.59,1:13:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the decision made
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.65,1:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,by the field itself
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.65,1:13:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to continue to exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.65,1:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But this
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.23,1:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,resulted in removal from the world
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.23,1:13:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,for some years.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.23,1:13:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It took years to learn how to
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.23,1:13:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,refunction again.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.90,1:13:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, even more rarely,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.90,1:13:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the capacity to realize
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.96,1:13:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,both realities
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.96,1:13:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,simultaneously
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.96,1:13:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and begin to
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.96,1:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,be able to relearn how to function
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.96,1:13:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world again
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.60,1:13:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,with some physical difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.60,1:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.60,1:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness as it evolves
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.60,1:13:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,on our planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.59,1:13:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.75,1:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop for a break at 10.30
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.75,1:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll resume.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.07,1:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What people would like to know,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.07,1:14:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they know we've calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.07,1:14:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the fields of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.29,1:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.93,1:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We started out to do 1,000
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.03,1:14:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.16,1:14:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we're up to 3,000 already.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.16,1:14:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not done with the list.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.51,1:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We started doing just
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.51,1:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so far we've done
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.51,1:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Americana, everything from
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.51,1:14:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,rock music to movie stars.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.51,1:14:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next section has to do
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.61,1:14:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,with spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.91,1:14:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The calibration of the various spiritual realities.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.91,1:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we do countries,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.20,1:14:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,international, we go into
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.20,1:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,paleontology, archaeology,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.20,1:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we go
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.96,1:14:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,into the arts, music,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.96,1:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,architecture, the great cathedrals,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.96,1:14:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,places of great spiritual interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.25,1:15:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the lectures
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.83,1:15:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sort of sharing with you
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.99,1:15:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,as we get to a certain point
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.99,1:15:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,we can make a transparency
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.05,1:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,which is semi-legible.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.05,1:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So today we have a semi-legible transparency.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.05,1:15:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anybody got any questions
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.98,1:15:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,about the distribution of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.98,1:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the implications
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.98,1:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the distribution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.98,1:15:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,when you see it country by country,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.00,1:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,region by region,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.00,1:15:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,continent by continent.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.04,1:15:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You get the implications
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.04,1:15:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for how to be
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.36,1:15:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in a world like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.61,1:15:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.61,1:15:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,why so much diplomacy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.61,1:15:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,completely fails.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.61,1:15:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You just miscalculate
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.03,1:15:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,where the other person is at.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.03,1:15:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, because of egotism
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.03,1:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody presumes that other people
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.03,1:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,think like you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.03,1:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't think like you do at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.03,1:15:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They think the way you speak is idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.28,1:15:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Freedom of speech is the most
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.28,1:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,idiotic thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.85,1:16:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing dumber than freedom of speech.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.92,1:16:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have the percentage
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.92,1:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of people who think
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.92,1:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that freedom of speech is
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.92,1:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.92,1:16:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fallacious is over 75%,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.34,1:16:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,80%, 85%, 90%.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.34,1:16:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Free speech.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.34,1:16:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,90% of free speech
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.30,1:16:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is totally fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.30,1:16:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we supposed to give up our life
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.62,1:16:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and genuflect
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.62,1:16:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,because occasionally
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.66,1:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,somebody tells the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.85,1:16:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,15% of the time?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.40,1:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.40,1:16:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,your butt is in hot water.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.13,1:16:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The editorials,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.23,1:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,everything is attacking everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.23,1:16:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You calibrate the level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.23,1:16:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that data
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.23,1:16:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and now a new picture of man's consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.23,1:17:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,begins to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.90,1:17:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To another country,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.90,1:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow such disorder,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.32,1:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,imagine how that's viewed
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.53,1:17:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,in Singapore.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.07,1:17:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rioting teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.87,1:17:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should they allow
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.69,1:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,civil disruption
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.69,1:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and threat to the peace of the community?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.69,1:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how a different community
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.69,1:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,views that.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.27,1:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dabbling idiots,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.27,1:17:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,causing unrest,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.56,1:17:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,throwing rocks,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.56,1:17:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,starting fires,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.56,1:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,calling forth the police,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.16,1:17:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,getting arrested,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.19,1:17:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,causing disruption
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.28,1:17:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.51,1:17:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,expounding some ideology
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.73,1:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,which if executed
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.73,1:17:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,would probably kill half the population
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.96,1:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and usually does
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.96,1:17:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,after the French Revolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.96,1:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the Russian Revolution,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.47,1:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,manage to slay most of the population.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.47,1:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a country then
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.68,1:18:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in which we worship free speech,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.68,1:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of which is fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.68,1:18:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting from a
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.22,1:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,primarily fallacious position,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.22,1:18:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we then seek to approach a country
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.22,1:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,whose calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.28,1:18:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't got the slight idea about
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.28,1:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and even if they could understand us
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.28,1:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,they would consider it ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.28,1:18:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.96,1:18:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You want us to have riots in the streets,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.96,1:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,drugs, crime and divorce rates
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.15,1:18:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,50% and a high abortion rate
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.15,1:18:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,for unwedded mothers?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.49,1:18:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.49,1:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the good of that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.49,1:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should we strive and die for that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.07,1:18:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you begin to see what you're up against.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.93,1:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We're smugly politically superior.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.93,1:18:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our system is good,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.93,1:18:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,the best and better
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.93,1:18:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and if other people don't like it
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.32,1:18:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll shove it down their throat
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.32,1:18:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or buy their way to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.02,1:19:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So the beginning of success
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.02,1:19:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in international affairs then
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.02,1:19:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is by attracting
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.02,1:19:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatly successful
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.02,1:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,people in society
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.02,1:19:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,are based on attraction
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.02,1:19:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and not promotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.02,1:19:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody tries to sell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.08,1:19:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They tell you this is how it was with me,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.08,1:19:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,this is what I learned
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.08,1:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is how my life is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.08,1:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Profound transformation.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.08,1:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably the best example,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.08,1:19:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the most successful spiritual endeavor
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.40,1:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world today
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.40,1:19:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is probably 12 step groups
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.40,1:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where you take a hopelessly pathologic
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.40,1:19:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,condition with a 100% death rate
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.62,1:19:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody ever recovered from it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.62,1:19:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,with a wet brain.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.78,1:19:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever recovered from it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.78,1:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now millions not only recover
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.78,1:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but become very famous people
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.78,1:19:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,governors and statesmen
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.12,1:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and great leaders of the world
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.12,1:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,once had a drinking problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.12,1:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So the spiritual power then
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.12,1:19:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of truth,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.12,1:19:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,pure spiritual truth then
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.19,1:20:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is enormously powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.35,1:20:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.54,1:20:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,we can influence other countries then
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.54,1:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is through the field
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.73,1:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,through spiritual upliftment
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.73,1:20:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a girl Friday
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.47,1:20:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,at a staff meeting
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.62,1:20:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,really into apathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.62,1:20:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The world would call it depression
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.62,1:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and it would look for psychological reasons
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.62,1:20:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,because the world thinks in terms of cause
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.62,1:20:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,what's causing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.12,1:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But to me I saw this girl
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.12,1:20:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,who had never had energy or love
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.25,1:20:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,poured into her.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.25,1:20:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that map of South Africa or Africa?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.25,1:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You still got it there?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.70,1:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.92,1:20:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.00,1:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.54,1:20:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not going to find logic or reason
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.54,1:20:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to be of any help whatsoever
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.54,1:20:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at Energy Fuel 50.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.08,1:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl at the staff meeting
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.84,1:20:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't have enough
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.84,1:21:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,energy
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.45,1:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,power of life
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.45,1:21:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to even learn how to control
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.45,1:21:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,her bladder and her bowel.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.90,1:21:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an infant.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.90,1:21:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And the problem is not depression
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.99,1:21:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem is apathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.21,1:21:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a poor energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.69,1:21:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady rocking in her chair
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.43,1:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and she did nothing but rock back and forth
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.43,1:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and look out the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.38,1:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't got enough energy
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.38,1:21:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to get up and move or eat
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.41,1:21:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.80,1:21:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to pour energy into them.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.37,1:21:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to control myself
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.37,1:21:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,because I could have really
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.37,1:21:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,opened up the dams
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.08,1:21:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and just flooded her with
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.08,1:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I tried to give her a flash
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.08,1:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,as she went by
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.10,1:21:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the joy of existence
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.10,1:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,comes out of
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.71,1:21:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the awareness of the presence within.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.71,1:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To have joy
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.76,1:22:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,she needs the energy of joy
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.76,1:22:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to come out of the bottom of the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.89,1:22:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm done with that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.89,1:22:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to the Calvary
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.34,1:22:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.85,1:22:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So depression is not where she's at.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.85,1:22:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's I'm sure here.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.85,1:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Apathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.40,1:22:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.40,1:22:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of going to school?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.40,1:22:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of keeping your room neat?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.40,1:22:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point of going to the dentist?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.78,1:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.32,1:22:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Total apathy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.32,1:22:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where South Africa is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.32,1:22:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where that girl is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.32,1:22:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's not South Africa
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.32,1:22:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but many places in Africa.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.32,1:22:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's where the girl is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.55,1:22:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.55,1:22:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's given up.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.55,1:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,God has no interest in her
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.55,1:22:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,naturally in despair.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.99,1:22:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's into despondency.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.37,1:22:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She tries to cover it up
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.37,1:22:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,with a certain social veneer
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.37,1:22:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but I see through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.37,1:23:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to hold the social veneer
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.44,1:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as she's forced to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.44,1:23:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She's going to pour energy into them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.44,1:23:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the energy you pour into them?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.44,1:23:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you love them.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.44,1:23:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You take this girl and say
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.44,1:23:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand that you get better.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.82,1:23:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she laughs.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.82,1:23:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She giggles.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.82,1:23:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody cares enough about her
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.82,1:23:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to be with her in a state of joyful ecstasy
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.82,1:23:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and pour forth that life energy into her.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.04,1:23:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The pouring forth of life energy then
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.04,1:23:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only way you can get things
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.04,1:23:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,out of the bottom of the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.04,1:23:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay so we're done with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.16,1:23:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So this sort of changes
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.16,1:23:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the way we see international politics.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.16,1:23:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It means
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.71,1:23:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,our first
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.80,1:23:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing we have to do
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.80,1:23:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is we have to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.80,1:23:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,where are they spiritually?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.80,1:23:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean in terms of
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.80,1:23:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.80,1:23:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What are the values of people at that level?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.70,1:23:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And address those values.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.70,1:23:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the crime bosses
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.70,1:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,are so successful in poverty areas.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.08,1:24:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only source of food.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.08,1:24:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.37,1:24:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They deplore it and call them criminals.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.37,1:24:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But where else are they going to get a handout?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.53,1:24:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the United States
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.82,1:24:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,we compromised didn't we
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.82,1:24:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in Afghanistan on the poppy fields.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.82,1:24:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.82,1:24:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We did a trade off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.36,1:24:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cheaper to let them raise the poppy
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.36,1:24:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and support themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.36,1:24:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,than to destroy the poppy
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.62,1:24:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've got to put them all on welfare.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.20,1:24:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed to me like that kind of a trade off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.67,1:24:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Afghanistan is the source
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.67,1:24:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of the world's supply of heroin.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.05,1:24:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The suffering and death brought about
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.05,1:24:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,by heroin worldwide
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.05,1:24:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is staggering.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.11,1:24:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the trade off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.07,1:24:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them keep the opium fuels
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.68,1:24:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in return for what we got for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.68,1:24:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.68,1:24:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like dropping an atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.68,1:24:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I didn't have to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.68,1:24:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The karma of all those dying heroin addicts
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.68,1:25:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,out of there because of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.68,1:25:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your trade off.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.09,1:25:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the taxpayers of America the money
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.09,1:25:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of supporting those people.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.09,1:25:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them support themselves with heroin and opium.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.32,1:25:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see how the thinking,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.32,1:25:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the determinants of judgment,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.32,1:25:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,morality,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.32,1:25:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the weighing of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.32,1:25:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it's not a matter of opposites.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.32,1:25:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that life is a matter of subtleties.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.32,1:25:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Slightly warmer to a little less warmer.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.32,1:25:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And a little bit more of this
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.32,1:25:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and a little bit more of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.32,1:25:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But even when you suddenly take this direction
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.32,1:25:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you only did it because
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.32,1:25:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there was one more feather.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.38,1:25:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The feather tipped the balance this way
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.38,1:25:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you decide to go that way.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.44,1:25:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this isn't the opposite of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.44,1:25:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only one feather away.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.70,1:25:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One feather away.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.92,1:25:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One more feather on this side they live.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.92,1:25:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One more feather on this side they die.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.92,1:25:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One more feather.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.92,1:25:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So we hold the feathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.44,1:25:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We hold the feathers.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.44,1:25:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtually evolved people
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.56,1:25:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,are the only source of real hope
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.56,1:26:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that people who live down here
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.69,1:26:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,have.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.95,1:26:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's by our pouring forth
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.95,1:26:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,our concern for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.28,1:26:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just our concern for them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.28,1:26:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Our concern for their welfare.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.28,1:26:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Our concern for their survival.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.73,1:26:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hope for their betterment.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.76,1:26:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when we send an invisible
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.76,1:26:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,love that they feel a stirring.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.76,1:26:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it's not a direct
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.76,1:26:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.21,1:26:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can change the rate at which
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.21,1:26:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,something rises in water
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.21,1:26:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,a cork rises in water
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.21,1:26:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,by changing the density of the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.21,1:26:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Every swimmer knows that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.21,1:26:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You float higher in the ocean
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.56,1:26:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,than you do in the Great Lakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.78,1:26:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up around the Great Lakes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.23,1:26:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No salt in the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.23,1:26:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Different buoyancy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.23,1:26:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we can do then
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.29,1:26:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is by the emanation
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.39,1:26:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of our own divinity forth
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.68,1:26:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,our knowingness of it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.68,1:26:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,our awareness of it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.68,1:27:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.68,1:27:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we change the specific gravity
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.19,1:27:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the density
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.19,1:27:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of the field
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.38,1:27:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore those people
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.41,1:27:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,become uplifted.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.41,1:27:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go there
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.60,1:27:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and say here I want you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.60,1:27:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop being poverty
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.60,1:27:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is food
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.67,1:27:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and now that solves it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.67,1:27:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Keeps them alive
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.67,1:27:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can die even worse
Dialogue: 0,1:27:26.40,1:27:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at a later date doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.40,1:27:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No. One has to change
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.40,1:27:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the total overall context.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.40,1:27:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And as we demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.40,1:27:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,in previous lectures
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.53,1:27:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that is scientifically valid.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.63,1:27:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hearts and flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.63,1:27:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The quantum mechanics of it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.63,1:27:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is that decision then.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.63,1:27:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you make a decision
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.63,1:27:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and collapse the wave function
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.36,1:27:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you can change it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.36,1:27:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The emanation of that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.36,1:27:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for those of you
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.36,1:27:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,who are interested
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.36,1:27:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the computer.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.78,1:28:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call that computer thing?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.78,1:28:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The e-mail world.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.39,1:28:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Internet world, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.39,1:28:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Henry Stapp.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.39,1:28:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor of physics at Berkeley
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.39,1:28:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,gives a very neat explanation
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.39,1:28:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,comprehensible by the intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.39,1:28:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with the opening into spiritual realities
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.39,1:28:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and how that could manifest
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.39,1:28:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and that their research
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.58,1:28:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,can help us
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.58,1:28:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.74,1:28:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that every time you make a decision
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.74,1:28:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in this direction
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.74,1:28:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,you increase the potentiality
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.74,1:28:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and the likelihood of its recurrence.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.74,1:28:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another principle
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.74,1:28:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in quantum mechanics
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.96,1:28:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that the more times you say yes
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.96,1:28:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to a thing
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.96,1:28:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you increase the probability
Dialogue: 0,1:28:45.04,1:28:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,of it being yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.04,1:28:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not 50-50 anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.14,1:28:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it becomes higher and higher
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.14,1:28:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,probability.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.14,1:28:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That works at a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.33,1:28:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not going to really change things
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.33,1:28:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because when they run out of food
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.33,1:29:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they're right back to the same fact
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.33,1:29:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that they've got nothing to raise food on.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.33,1:29:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When they run out of this bag of flour
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.33,1:29:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,they're right back to starvation again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.33,1:29:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try to lift
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.62,1:29:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness of all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.62,1:29:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,by evolving our own.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.62,1:29:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.29,1:29:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to the presence of God
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.29,1:29:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.29,1:29:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very powerful tool.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.35,1:29:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It already exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.35,1:29:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to create it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.56,1:29:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It already exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:33.22,1:29:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is willing to surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.22,1:29:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,everything for God
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.22,1:29:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,even life itself
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.64,1:29:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,already exists within you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.20,1:29:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And much to your surprise
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.20,1:29:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes up in great power
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.20,1:29:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when you didn't even know it was there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.20,1:29:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At the last moment
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.20,1:29:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you're faced with surrendering
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.20,1:29:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,life itself to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.58,1:30:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To thee, O God, do I surrender this life.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.24,1:30:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion to do so
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.87,1:30:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is already present.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.09,1:30:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's like a shock
Dialogue: 0,1:30:13.92,1:30:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,when it comes up and you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.92,1:30:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have within you
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.18,1:30:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the power to do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.52,1:30:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only to surrender the details of life
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.52,1:30:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to dissolve the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.52,1:30:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,transcend the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.97,1:30:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but eventually the very core
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.97,1:30:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you think is you
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.37,1:30:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as you all sit there
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.37,1:30:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you profoundly believe
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.37,1:30:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is you
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.39,1:30:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,your reality
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.39,1:30:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and who you are
Dialogue: 0,1:30:46.71,1:30:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially, not intellectually
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.25,1:30:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the doorway
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.60,1:30:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,one surrenders completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.88,1:30:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is the doorway to enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.58,1:31:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the limitation
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.16,1:31:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,of the commitment
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.92,1:31:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't happen all that often.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.92,1:31:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Devotional non-duality means
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.68,1:31:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,one is devoted to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.68,1:31:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,devoted to the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.68,1:31:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll get to more of the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.03,1:31:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,after we have a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.92,1:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is necessary
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.80,1:31:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.80,1:31:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,already exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.57,1:31:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,To reach a state of divine
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.60,1:31:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,unconditional lovingness
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.60,1:31:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is quite sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.60,1:31:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.60,1:31:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lotusland Buddhism
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.60,1:31:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,which teaches pretty much the same
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.60,1:31:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as Christianity then says
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.70,1:31:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,once you've reached the level of unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.70,1:31:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the way is certain
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.70,1:31:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.66,1:31:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And so we'll take a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.04,1:32:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Those of you who have read
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.77,1:32:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the books and attended lectures
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.77,1:32:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,know that the pathway
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.32,1:32:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the direct pathway to God is radical.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.32,1:32:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a radical devotion
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.72,1:32:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to truth above all else.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.72,1:32:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that so important?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.43,1:32:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Because untruth stands
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.43,1:32:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,in the way of love
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.43,1:33:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who seek to reach God through love
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.43,1:33:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,constantly run into blocks.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.87,1:33:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So we try to resolve the blocks
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.87,1:33:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so that when devotion
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.14,1:33:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,comes up there's nothing to obstruct it
Dialogue: 0,1:33:13.14,1:33:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and when it does it comes like
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.14,1:33:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,like a dam just broke
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.24,1:33:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no stopping it.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.99,1:33:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll get rid of duality
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.99,1:33:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,today and the next
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.99,1:33:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,less than a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.04,1:33:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.93,1:33:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you like chocolate doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,1:33:38.93,1:33:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to hate vanilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.16,1:33:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That resolves all your political problems
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.16,1:33:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,right there.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.87,1:33:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people like chocolate
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.87,1:33:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,some people like vanilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.87,1:33:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.40,1:34:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.06,1:34:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.15,1:34:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The best way, the fastest way
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.15,1:34:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to reach the presence within
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.40,1:34:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is through joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.45,1:34:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Joy, happiness,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.45,1:34:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,thankfulness, gratitude,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.32,1:34:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.72,1:34:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you hear those are all positive things.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.72,1:34:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different than
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.80,1:34:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,sackcloth and ashes,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.80,1:34:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,self-flagellation, agony, suffering,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.80,1:34:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,sin. It's a different pathway.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.16,1:34:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.88,1:34:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to it if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.40,1:34:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's certainly why I became
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.40,1:34:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,an atheist when I was a young age.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.40,1:34:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because it
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.48,1:34:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,conflicted with an inner knowingness
Dialogue: 0,1:34:55.48,1:34:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,of the truth that the presence
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.48,1:34:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with that which is
Dialogue: 0,1:34:59.48,1:35:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,ecstatic, exquisite,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.48,1:35:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,joyful.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.46,1:35:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So we look at the
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.84,1:35:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,antecedent of it. We looked at the world
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.84,1:35:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,today and we see how it's laid out at this point
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.84,1:35:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,with the advancement of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.84,1:35:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We see the distribution of
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.32,1:35:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness. You understand
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.18,1:35:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the profundity of the discovery
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.18,1:35:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because we can take
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.76,1:35:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the calibrated levels of consciousness of every
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.76,1:35:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,country and every region.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.76,1:35:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do that with every
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.76,1:35:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,antecedent of man, Neanderthal man,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.76,1:35:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Homo erectus.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.76,1:35:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This week's Time magazine
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.20,1:35:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,had a new one, 160,000 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.20,1:35:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't calibrate
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.72,1:35:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,his level of consciousness yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.29,1:35:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do so now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.17,1:35:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an antecedent.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.33,1:35:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.59,1:35:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an antecedent of Homo sapiens.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.59,1:35:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And he is an early Homo sapiens.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.68,1:36:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And his consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.67,1:36:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is over 100.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.67,1:36:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His consciousness is over 70.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.88,1:36:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,His consciousness is over
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.81,1:36:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,65.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.84,1:36:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His consciousness is over 60.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:15.48,1:36:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His consciousness is over 55.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.48,1:36:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He better get up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.48,1:36:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.71,1:36:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but you see the beginning of the structure
Dialogue: 0,1:36:28.71,1:36:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of Homo sapiens.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.71,1:36:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And then consciousness catches up with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.71,1:36:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.28,1:36:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.97,1:36:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.18,1:36:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty with the calibrated levels
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.18,1:36:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.01,1:36:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it can get you into a polarized position
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.01,1:36:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which makes you go weak,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.01,1:37:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that which makes you go strong,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.01,1:37:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is below 200,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.01,1:37:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.01,1:37:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth versus falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.41,1:37:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the downside of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.41,1:37:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why I mentioned chocolate and vanilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.41,1:37:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you like chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.48,1:37:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean you have to make vanilla wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.48,1:37:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because vanilla had to first become vanilla
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.48,1:37:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,before it could become chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.88,1:37:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to have ice cream before you could flavor it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.88,1:37:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.39,1:37:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So vanilla is below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.39,1:37:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's early antecedent Homo sapiens.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.39,1:37:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he rises
Dialogue: 0,1:37:34.39,1:37:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,in his level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.39,1:37:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and it becomes chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.38,1:37:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.08,1:37:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to get out of polarization.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.08,1:37:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember chocolate and vanilla
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.08,1:37:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because it will get you right out of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.08,1:37:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see that your mind is automatically reverting back to
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.08,1:37:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we're right therefore they're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.08,1:37:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they like chocolate, we like vanilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.59,1:37:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We as societies think that free speech is idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.59,1:38:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It leads to insurrection.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.84,1:38:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It leads to death.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.84,1:38:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It leads to revolt.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.28,1:38:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It leads to destruction of the economy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.04,1:38:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.13,1:38:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they like chocolate and we like vanilla.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.13,1:38:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to feel that you can blabber anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.13,1:38:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.06,1:38:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean our country is more entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.06,1:38:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can only say what's been approved
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.06,1:38:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,how tedious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.32,1:38:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.80,1:38:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the books I've written are being looked at
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.96,1:38:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in China and they have a thought police there
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.96,1:38:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,they have to examine them and see
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.96,1:38:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,whether or not they're permissible
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.96,1:38:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to publish in China.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.40,1:38:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're hoping that they won't notice
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.40,1:38:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual and religious and they just pay attention
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.40,1:38:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.40,1:38:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Consciousness may slip by the censors.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.40,1:38:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright so today I thought we would
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.39,1:39:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,share where we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.70,1:39:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You see you can go back now in the maps
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.70,1:39:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have and check them out
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.70,1:39:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,century by century.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.76,1:39:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this whole map.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.76,1:39:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to picture this.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.76,1:39:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a wonderment of movies
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.89,1:39:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,like a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.31,1:39:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say each one of those calibrations
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.31,1:39:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,has a color.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:20.31,1:39:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets darker and lighter let's say.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.31,1:39:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Or more green and more yellow.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:24.66,1:39:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you go back 500 years
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.11,1:39:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and do these same areas.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.11,1:39:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You go back another 100 years and do the same areas.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.11,1:39:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You go back and back and back through time.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.45,1:39:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See what a fascinating map that would make?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.45,1:39:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,First you see light begin to appear.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.45,1:39:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it comes out light yellow.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.45,1:39:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it starts to turn green.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.45,1:39:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And over here you see it turn red.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.45,1:39:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it turns black.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.86,1:39:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And here it shines forth
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.86,1:39:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like a moving hologram over time.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.86,1:39:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See what you can do with that with graphics.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.24,1:39:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the technology exists to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.10,1:40:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So what were the levels of these countries
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.10,1:40:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,century by century?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.80,1:40:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can see the
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.96,1:40:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,men begin to appear.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.96,1:40:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Homo sapiens begin to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.96,1:40:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.40,1:40:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,appear and then you see it shine forth
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.40,1:40:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,most brilliantly in today's world
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.40,1:40:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in North America
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.40,1:40:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and in America in particular.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.40,1:40:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.79,1:40:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we're the advancing front
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.79,1:40:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,of the evolution of human consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.79,1:40:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrates higher than any country.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.48,1:40:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means
Dialogue: 0,1:40:35.46,1:40:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that we don't like idiots.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.46,1:40:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.44,1:40:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,vanilla and chocolate is mixed together
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.44,1:40:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so you get mocha.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.87,1:40:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the difference is that
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.87,1:40:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I said
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.60,1:40:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the best thing we can do for the world
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.60,1:40:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is to hold them in our thoughts and prayers
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.89,1:41:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is because
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.15,1:41:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the higher the calibrated level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.15,1:41:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the greater its power.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.15,1:41:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So numerically
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.56,1:41:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,there may be many below 200
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.56,1:41:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but their relative power
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.63,1:41:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is weak because
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.63,1:41:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,one person at 600
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.72,1:41:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,counterbalances
Dialogue: 0,1:41:18.72,1:41:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,most of humanity
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.72,1:41:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and one at 1000
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.72,1:41:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,really counterbalances
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.72,1:41:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.72,1:41:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So consequently
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.85,1:41:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the more advanced we become
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.85,1:41:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and hold such people in mind
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.85,1:41:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,compassionate
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.85,1:41:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for their suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:41:37.56,1:41:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then the power of that intention
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.56,1:41:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is such that we actually
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.56,1:41:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,lift the life of people
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.39,1:41:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,at the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.87,1:41:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.87,1:41:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or if that's airy-fairy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.08,1:41:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona doesn't like airy-fairy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.08,1:41:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So we just said it's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.08,1:42:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The devotion of even a group like this
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.04,1:42:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,will have a measurable effect
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.20,1:42:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on the consciousness level
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.20,1:42:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,of those at the bottom of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.20,1:42:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The consciousness of this group
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.35,1:42:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,here
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.73,1:42:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,affects those at the bottom of the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.44,1:42:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One day
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.47,1:42:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of not having the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.47,1:42:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to even feed yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.50,1:42:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly you care enough to feed yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:22.92,1:42:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Many at the bottom of the barrel
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.92,1:42:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,do not even have the energy
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.92,1:42:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to feed themselves.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.92,1:42:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They will starve to death
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.27,1:42:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,laying right next to the food.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.58,1:42:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to believe but it's so.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.58,1:42:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we include them
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.58,1:42:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,in our intention
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.58,1:42:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritual intention is where your power is
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.71,1:42:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that will save you flying over there
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.28,1:42:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and marching in parades
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.68,1:42:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,because you affect the field
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.68,1:42:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and because you affect the field
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.68,1:42:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you affect that which is real.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.16,1:42:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is real. That which is permanent.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:59.16,1:43:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has great power.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.95,1:43:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we just transcended
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.95,1:43:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego and the intellect
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.01,1:43:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and we did a lot already.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.01,1:43:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's see how this
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.01,1:43:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,evolved over time
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.01,1:43:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because we also
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.01,1:43:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrated, I don't know
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.27,1:43:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,like about 600
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.27,1:43:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual teachers, religions
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.27,1:43:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,things that
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.65,1:43:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a constant mail
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.65,1:43:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,about these things
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.65,1:43:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore we thought we'd do some.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.65,1:43:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's start with one.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.97,1:43:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,People ask, you know
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.87,1:43:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,endlessly. We've got stacks
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.87,1:43:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,of mail this high.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.57,1:43:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This teacher, that guru, that book
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.83,1:43:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,this spiritual discipline,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.83,1:43:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,this religion. Now where do they
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.02,1:43:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate? Well
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.02,1:43:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,we've reached the
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.02,1:43:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,at least this group has reached the level
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.02,1:43:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of dedication to truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.24,1:43:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll give you a caveat.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.24,1:43:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who belongs to a
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.24,1:44:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,rigid religion, you better
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.07,1:44:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,leave now. Alright, so we
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.02,1:44:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,began calibrating
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.18,1:44:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we all start out
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.40,1:44:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in the same place as
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.40,1:44:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to the nature of God.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.17,1:44:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book I, I think
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.17,1:44:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we summarized what we did at Creative Life
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.17,1:44:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think chapter 10 calibrates it
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.17,1:44:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a thousand. The exact nature
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.88,1:44:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of God. I think we made 24
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.88,1:44:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,or 28 statements about the exact nature
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.88,1:44:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,of God. In the entire group
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.88,1:44:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we all did kinesiology together
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.88,1:44:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was 100%
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.58,1:44:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,agreement about the truth of every single
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.58,1:44:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,statement, which is videotaped
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.80,1:44:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,documented forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.47,1:44:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to go back to scriptures that
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.47,1:44:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,are a thousand years old
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.47,1:44:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,all about dead people and geographic
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.47,1:44:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,places you're never going to visit and never have been.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.47,1:45:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The evidence for the existence
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.84,1:45:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and the reality of God is right here
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.84,1:45:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,now. Right here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.09,1:45:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to rely on
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.09,1:45:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,history. Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.40,1:45:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So to make sure we're all in the same
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.40,1:45:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,place, we have to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.40,1:45:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what we mean by God and so we asked
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.40,1:45:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the various names of God
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.40,1:45:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and what do they calibrate?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.04,1:45:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The verification of spiritual realities.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:26.04,1:45:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Man has had no way to verify
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.38,1:45:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual reality. The only person who can
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.38,1:45:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,verify spiritual reality is a mystic.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.38,1:45:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody else is just talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.38,1:45:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What they heard, what they read in
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.10,1:45:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,some old book. What good does that
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.16,1:45:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,do you? You don't get enlightened
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.70,1:45:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,2000 years back in retrospect.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.70,1:45:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It happens here now folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.70,1:45:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.70,1:45:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,God has to be an
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.70,1:45:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,existent, verifiable,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.70,1:46:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential, subjective
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.70,1:46:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,reality which can
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.02,1:46:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,be experienced in the here and now.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:06.02,1:46:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise it's just talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.02,1:46:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is full of talking
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.27,1:46:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,about God. Alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:13.43,1:46:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we said what is
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.78,1:46:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy field of
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.78,1:46:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,the concept of God transcendent?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.97,1:46:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.68,1:46:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,God infinity, the creator?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.68,1:46:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty God.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.42,1:46:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Creator of heaven and earth
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.42,1:46:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and of all things visible and invisible
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.42,1:46:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,through his son our Lord Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,1:46:36.42,1:46:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:38.42,1:46:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We do bless this endeavor. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.34,1:46:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All those terms are infinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.34,1:46:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The supreme,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.79,1:46:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which you hear from Krishna.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:48.79,1:46:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The supreme, Allah, the God of
Dialogue: 0,1:46:50.85,1:46:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Muslims, Shiva,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.01,1:46:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Brahman, all the names for God,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:55.01,1:46:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Vishnu. You ask what do they
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.01,1:46:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate? God of Moses
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.01,1:47:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I wrote that in.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.52,1:47:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to forget
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.52,1:47:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Abraham. All of them
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.64,1:47:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,infinity. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.64,1:47:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that is God as transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:10.64,1:47:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite creator
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.25,1:47:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.02,1:47:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The unmanifest becoming manifest
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.02,1:47:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,as creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.14,1:47:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite energy field
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.14,1:47:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to which all form
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.99,1:47:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,responds automatically
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.99,1:47:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as a quality
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.63,1:47:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:34.63,1:47:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God is imminent then
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.16,1:47:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is the God of the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.16,1:47:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The one that we strive
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.06,1:47:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for in these classes.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.57,1:47:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's referred to
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.63,1:47:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,in Sanskrit as God imminent
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.63,1:47:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,as the Purusa.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.72,1:47:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As a spiritual teacher is talking
Dialogue: 0,1:47:54.72,1:47:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,once comes the wording,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.72,1:47:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,understanding, the conceptualization,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.72,1:48:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,etc. It happens
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.72,1:48:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,spontaneously of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.78,1:48:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no decision or thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.78,1:48:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,To use a bad word
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.52,1:48:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is not a decision one makes
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.68,1:48:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when hears it.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:13.03,1:48:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.28,1:48:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,said. Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.02,1:48:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening of its own spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.02,1:48:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you reach a certain
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.53,1:48:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,level of realization
Dialogue: 0,1:48:24.53,1:48:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you realize that
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.53,1:48:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that is the state of reality
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.53,1:48:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:30.53,1:48:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no you
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.72,1:48:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,deciding to sit in the chair
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.72,1:48:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or trying to understand this
Dialogue: 0,1:48:36.72,1:48:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,or think your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.65,1:48:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:42.68,1:48:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You as this little iron filing
Dialogue: 0,1:48:44.68,1:48:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,through your own spiritual intention
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.68,1:48:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,bring yourself into a certain field
Dialogue: 0,1:48:48.68,1:48:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in which all that phenomena
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.68,1:48:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is happening autonomously,
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.68,1:48:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,automatically, and perfectly of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.96,1:48:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't require you to even do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.96,1:49:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That gets rid of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:04.71,1:49:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that there is a person
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.71,1:49:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,speaking all these words
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.71,1:49:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,would be the height of success of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.03,1:49:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego would say,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:13.03,1:49:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the author of all that you do think
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.03,1:49:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:17.03,1:49:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego is not the author of experience.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.03,1:49:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.32,1:49:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that gets filtered through.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.73,1:49:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the self
Dialogue: 0,1:49:25.92,1:49:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we hear the realization of the self
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.92,1:49:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,many spiritual treatises
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.92,1:49:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,are called realization of the self.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.46,1:49:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The self with a capital S then
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.46,1:49:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is God immanent, present
Dialogue: 0,1:49:37.46,1:49:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and it speaks as the
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.46,1:49:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Purusha of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.46,1:49:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It speaks as that.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.81,1:49:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's merely the voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:45.88,1:49:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Another term for it is Atman.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.88,1:49:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And this
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.36,1:49:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is supposed to be down below here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:52.36,1:49:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I want to contrast
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.84,1:49:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,God immanent and transcendent
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.84,1:49:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because there is great argumentation.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:58.93,1:50:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Catholic Church is divided
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.93,1:50:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,East and West, the Greek Orthodox
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.93,1:50:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Roman Church
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.16,1:50:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,over the understanding of
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.16,1:50:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,some of these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.28,1:50:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So they are very divisive
Dialogue: 0,1:50:11.28,1:50:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,whether the ultimate reality is
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.28,1:50:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God transcendent or
Dialogue: 0,1:50:15.28,1:50:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God immanent
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.28,1:50:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,can lead to huge schisms within the church.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:19.28,1:50:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And in reality
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.28,1:50:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't experience God as transcendent.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.28,1:50:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.80,1:50:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,experience God as immanent.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.80,1:50:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk about God as transcendent
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.80,1:50:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore theology goes up to about
Dialogue: 0,1:50:31.80,1:50:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,460 and then it stops there.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.18,1:50:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So theology
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.18,1:50:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has perfected the talking-ness about it
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.18,1:50:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:50:42.68,1:50:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the ways to God is through philosophy
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.68,1:50:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you are serious about philosophy
Dialogue: 0,1:50:46.68,1:50:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it will take you to epistemology.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.68,1:50:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Epistemology will take you
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.93,1:50:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to the transference
Dialogue: 0,1:50:53.70,1:50:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,of the source of the reality
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.70,1:50:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of the source of the realization
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.73,1:50:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of reality from objective to subjective
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.73,1:51:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and there you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:01.73,1:51:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can find God if you
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.66,1:51:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,follow philosophy to its bitter end
Dialogue: 0,1:51:06.66,1:51:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,where you finally give up classical
Dialogue: 0,1:51:08.66,1:51:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,philosophy and you realize
Dialogue: 0,1:51:10.69,1:51:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that only subjectivity
Dialogue: 0,1:51:14.58,1:51:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,can be verified.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:16.64,1:51:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One cannot verify
Dialogue: 0,1:51:20.05,1:51:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,any objectivity at all
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.05,1:51:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,anywhere.
